hadiths[2]{hadithnumber,text,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
346,"""He (Allah bless him and give him peace) was more bashful than the virgin in her boudoir, and when he disapproved of something, we knew it from the expression on his face.”",,,49061,"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri said:",Chapter 49
347,"“I never looked at the private parts of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace).” (Or she said: “I never saw the private parts of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace).”",,,49062,"'A’isha said:",Chapter 49
